OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FHot-flushes menopause drug 
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fapproved in UK             
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, A new type of non-hormonal menopause   
OL,6, treatment has been approved in the UK, 
OL,7, for hot flushes and night sweats.      
OL,9,FThe daily pill, Veoza - or fezolinetant
OL,10,F- works on the brain's                 
OL,11,Ftemperature-control centre to alleviate
OL,12,Fthese troubling symptoms.              
OL,14,FAt least one in four women going       
OL,15,Fthrough the menopause experiences them 
OL,16,F- more than a million people in the UK 
OL,17,F- experts estimate.                    
OL,19,FThe drug has not yet been recommended  
OL,20,Ffor the NHS to prescribe though.       
